        "content": "<p>I'm not familiar with this area but is this different from <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=CategoryTheory.GrothendieckTopology#doc\">docs#CategoryTheory.GrothendieckTopology</a> ?</p>",
