        "content": "<p>It is one specific construction of a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=CategoryTheory.GrothendieckTopology#doc\">docs#CategoryTheory.GrothendieckTopology</a> <span aria-label=\"slight smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"slight smile\">:slight_smile:</span> just like the cofinite topology would be one particular construction of a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=TopologicalSpace#doc\">docs#TopologicalSpace</a></p>",
        "id": 534842315,
